### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@dishId = <pega_el_id_del_plato>

### ─────────────────────────────
### DISHES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear plato TRADITIONAL (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Milanesa con puré",
  "description": "Milanesa de carne con puré de papas",
  "menu_type": "TRADITIONAL"
}

###

### Crear plato HEALTHY (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Tarta de jamón y queso",
  "description": "Tarta integral con jamón y queso",
  "menu_type": "HEALTHY"
}

###

### Crear plato VEGETARIAN (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Risotto de hongos",
  "description": "Risotto cremoso con hongos salteados",
  "menu_type": "VEGETARIAN"
}

###

### Listar todos los platos
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos por tipo — TRADITIONAL
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?menu_type=TRADITIONAL
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos por tipo — HEALTHY
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?menu_type=HEALTHY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos por tipo — VEGETARIAN
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?menu_type=VEGETARIAN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener plato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes/one?dishId={{dishId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar plato (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/dishes/{{dishId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Milanesa con puré actualizada",
  "description": "Descripción actualizada",
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar plato (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/dishes/{{dishId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Milanesa con puré",
  "description": "Milanesa de carne",
  "active": false
}

###

### Eliminar plato (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/dishes/{{dishId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
